			*** View Child
		
		
	-->	ViewChild is a most used decorators and has many many important use cases.
	
	-->	We can use @viewChild to inject a reference to existing component or DOM element.
	
	-->	@viewChild gets loaded after ngAfterViewInit() method.
			-- don't write this oninit
	
	-->	viewChild decorator is used when we want to get any other component or element of one component to another component
	
	
